quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,Ndifunga ngelanga nangokumenyezela kwalo
  91,2,Nangenyanga xa ililandela
  91,3,Nangemini xa ibonisa ukukhazimla kwalo (ilanga)
  91,4,Nangobusuku xa buligquma
  91,5,Nangezulu nangaloWo Walakhayo
  91,6,Nangomhlaba nangaloWo Wawandlalayo
  91,7,Nangomphefulo nangaloWo Wawufezekisayo
  91,8,Waza kananjalo Wawubonisa okungawulungelanga noko kuwulungeleyo
  91,9,Inene uphumelele lowo uwuhlambululayo
  91,10,Akaphumelelanga lowo uwungcolisayo
  91,11,(Abantu) bakwaThamûd babaphikisa (abaProfeti babo) ngokugabadela kwabo
  91,12,Xa oyena mntu wayengcole kakhulu phakathi kwabo waphuma (waya kubulala imazi yenkamela)
  91,13,"Kodwa uMthunywa ka-Allâh (uSâlih) wathi kubo: “Ze nilumke! (Noyike isihelegu esiya kunihlela), yimazi yenkamela ka-Allâh le, ningayibulali okanye niyithintele ekuseleni amanzi wayo"
  91,14,"Bamphikisa ke bayibulala. Ngoko ke iNkosi yabo Yabatshabalalisa ngenxa yesono sabo, Yabenza batshabalala ngokulinganayo (abazizityebi nabangamahlwempu phakathi kwabo abangakholwayo)"
  91,15,Kwaye uAllâh Azanga Abe naloyiko lweziphumo zako oko